<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="deep-adj">deep <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /diːp/    美 /diːp/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>深的</strong></h4>
<p>反 shallow </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The swimming pool has a deep end and a shallow end for kids.
这个游泳池的一端是深水区，一端是供小孩用的浅水区。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>（呼吸）深深的；（声音）低沉的；（颜色） 深的</strong></h4>
<p>反 light </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She took a deep breath and began to speak.
她深吸了一口气，然后开始讲话。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a deep voice
低沉的声音</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a deep red coat 
深红色外套</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>(程度) 深的；深奥的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a deep impression 
深刻的印象</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>fall into a deep sleep 
酣然入睡</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>be <strong>in deep trouble</strong>
麻烦大了</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What I want to tell you is the deep love and respect I have for my parents. 
我要告诉你的是我对父母深深的爱和尊敬。</p><footer> 2013 天津</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His books are too deep for me. 
他的书对我来说太深奥了。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>深陷的；专注的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>be deep in mud 
深陷泥潭</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In the painting, a young woman sits alone and is <strong>deep in thought</strong>. 
画中的年轻女子独自静坐，陷入沉思。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>deepen /'diːpən/ v   </p></div>